* to allow further changes without having to redfine.

  CALL METHOD super->if_ish_component~cancel
    EXPORTING
      i_authority_check = i_authority_check
      i_check_only      = i_check_only
      i_vma             = i_vma
      i_reason          = i_reason
    IMPORTING
